a tiny benchmarking suite for the classic snake game.
created in collaboration with @pinouchon from tufalabs.ai.

             ____
            / . .\
            \  ---<
             \  /
   __________/ /
-=:___________/

usage:

   $ uv run src/snake.py
   $ uv run src/snake.py --cli --runs 5
   $ uv run --with pytest pytest test

example output of the solver playing the game:
  
  ┌Score: 9────────────────────┐
  │███████████                 │
  │█                           │
  │                            │
  │                            │
  │     ó                      │
  └────────────────────────────┘
